94
00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:39.100
So loss of Y is a during lifetime acquired

95
00:05:39.140 --> 00:05:40.900
mutation. It happens during

96
00:05:42.460 --> 00:05:46.220
mitotic errors leading to aneuploidic cells with

