00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:45.960
But moving back to the Y chromosome loss.

117
00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:50.140
So when this occurs in the hematopoietic stem cells pool, it will

118
00:06:50.200 --> 00:06:52.160
