It varies between ethnicities and so forth, but roughly

144
00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.620
quite similar.

145
00:08:21.620 --> 00:08:23.320
Depends also on technologies and stuff.

146
00:08:24.260 --> 00:08:27.620
But if we combine this with data on demographics

