228
00:12:49.236 --> 00:12:53.046
So in addition to all-cause mortality, we also

229
00:12:53.076 --> 00:12:54.876
identified increased risk for cancer.

230
00:12:55.736 --> 00:12:59.316
So both cancer mortality overall and solid tumors.

231
00:12:59.346 --> 00:13:03.276
And this has been replicated quite well during the last decade, I would

232
00:13:03.336 --> 00:13:06.856
