00:13:28.916 --> 00:13:32.716
Ester and Dan will cover, is kind of the loss of

241
00:13:32.816 --> 00:13:35.236
Y in the cancer cells, which is also extremely frequent.

242
00:13:36.436 --> 00:13:40.216
So you will see this slide with better resolution soon and discussed by, in

