00:13:44.176 --> 00:13:46.556
I will not spoil too much, but it's very important

245
00:13:47.556 --> 00:13:49.576
in tumor biology, of course.

246
00:13:51.916 --> 00:13:55.166
So in addition to blood and cancer genomes,

247
00:13:56.116 --> 00:13:58.696
loss of Y is also common in other tissues, it appears.

248
00:13:59.516 --> 00:14:03.296
So it's enriched in microglia in Alzheimer patients and

