00:14:17.976 --> 00:14:19.356
So it's all over the place.

254
00:14:21.516 --> 00:14:23.436
So adding IPF to this list,

255
00:14:24.276 --> 00:14:26.206
actually, the risk

256
00:14:26.256 --> 00:14:30.056
for all major causes of

257
00:14:30.076 --> 00:14:33.296
death is associated with loss of Y, including the biggest killers,

258
00:14:33.596 --> 00:14:36.165
